carepal-demo/
# Ignore Claude scratch dirs, but share team-wide settings + hooks so the
# test-discipline enforcement applies to every contributor's local Claude
# sessions. Pattern: ignore everything under .claude/ first, then negate the
# specific files we want tracked. (Negating won't work if the parent dir is
# wholly ignored, so we use .claude/* not .claude/.)
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/hooks/
.claude/hooks/*
!.claude/hooks/check-tests.mjs

# Personal working files (call transcripts, draft notes, scratch diagrams) - not part of the tool.
# See docs/PROJECT_OVERVIEW.md "Repo conventions" for the convention.
/Transcipts/
/flowy/
/personal/
*.local.docx
*accessKeys*

